(241, '3rd', '2023', 'August', '2', 'Research', 'Prepared  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental for SGOD Chief review and SDS Approval.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'SEPS Planning and Research Frontline Services, performed routinely.', 'August 7-11, 2023', 'August 7-11, 2023', 'research', 'https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1a7l5pt29AJgwdaTjtTwi8biEYYVKr2x7?usp=sharing', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\n', 'Number of Approval Letters Prepared', '6', '6', '100%', 'Frontline services in research management: Evaluate requests for research permits and prepare  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research based on client demand. This task is part of the key responsibility areas (KRA) for research governance. It ensures that all research activities conducted in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental have been thoroughly reviewed and approved, maintaining high research standards. ', 'SGOD'),
(242, '1st', '2024', 'February', '3', 'Research', 'Provided Technical Assistance Services to Division Researchers in the Crafting of Basic/Action Research  Proposals/Studies.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Online & Face to Face TA Sessions', 'February 12-16, 2024', 'February 12-16, 2024', 'research', 'Note: MOVs via VTC Platform/ FB Messenger/GMail and SMS. \r\n', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\nKRA 4. Technical Assistance\r\n\r\n', 'Number of Researchers /Research Proposals/Studies  given Technical Assistance', '8', '8', '100%', 'Frontline Technical Assistance services of SEPS Planning and Research based on client requests. Successfully provided technical assistance to the division researchers as needed, focusing on the development of basic and action research proposals/studies. Each researcher had unique needs, and tailored assistance was provided accordingly. This included aspects such as research design, data analysis techniques, and best practices for academic writing. The guidance provided contributed significantly to the enhancement of research proposals/studies, and the researchers are now better equipped to conduct their respective studies. Feedback from the researchers was positive, with many expressing gratitude for the insightful assistance. Looking forward to seeing the impactful outcomes these research studies will bring to the education sector in our division.', 'SGOD'),
