(254, '2nd', '2023', 'September', '1', 'Research', 'Prepared 13 Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental for SGOD Chief review and SDS Approval.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'SEPS Planning and Research Frontline Services, performed routinely.', 'Sep. 4-8, 2023', 'Sep. 4-8, 2023', 'research', 'https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1a7l5pt29AJgwdaTjtTwi8biEYYVKr2x7?usp=sharing', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\n', 'Number of Approval Letters Prepared', '6', '6', '100%', 'Frontline services in research management: Evaluate requests for research permits and prepare  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research based on client demand.', 'SGOD'),
(255, '2nd', '2023', 'June', '4', 'Research', 'Facilitated and Evaluated  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental Via Online Google Form', 'Accomplishment', '', 'SEPS Planning and Research Frontline Services, performed routinely.', 'June 19-23, 2023', 'June 19-23, 2023', 'research', 'https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1V4njudbYXsdzFebqct_vBU-RSN9WovteWVftzSyXMKY/edit?usp=sharing', 'KRA 2. Research\r\n\r\n*Frontline Services to Researchers - Issuance of Permits to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental subject for SGOD Chief Review and SDS Approval ', 'Number of Permits Reviewed and Approved', '7', '7', '100%', 'Achieved a 100% completion rate in evaluating and approving permits for research, demonstrating our commitment to support and encourage research in the Division. This activity aligns with our Key Result Area (KRA) in research and emphasizes our proactive approach in promoting research culture. It also highlights our efficiency in handling and processing such requests, thereby ensuring researchers can begin their work without unnecessary delays. The approved research could contribute to the furth', 'SGOD'),
(256, '2nd', '2023', 'June', '4', 'Research', 'Provided Resource Speaker and Technical Assistance Services as Schools Division Research Management Committee Member in the conduct of : Division Blended Seminar Workshop in Crafting Research (Research Training Batch- 3  CY2023) ', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Blended Mode: at Baywalk Hotel Mati & via Zoom VTC Platform.', 'June 17-18, 2023', 'June 17-18, 2023', 'research', 'https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ccxSXdJsWHFyrkndjMUiMfb2Z-L0_04gl71P0dVKjZ8/edit?usp=sharing', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\nKRA 4. Technical Assistance\r\nThis activity signifies the crucial role of the Schools Division Research Management Committee in enhancing the capacity of educators in crafting quality research. The blending mode of delivery ensured the reach to a wider audience amidst the prevailing circumstances.\r\n\r\n', 'Number of Seminar Workshops Assisted and Facilitated', '1', '1', '100%', 'Frontline  Training Support/Technical Assistance Services of SEPS Planning and Research based on client requests.  Frontline Training Support/Technical Assistance Services of SEPS Planning and Research were successfully executed, reflected in the achievement of the target. The seminar workshop facilitated is crucial for skill enhancement in research among the educators.', 'SGOD'),
(257, '1st', '2024', 'January', '2', 'Research', 'Attended the Regional Virtual Planning Conference for Preparation for PIR FY 2023 via MS Teams.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Virtual via MS Teams', 'January 5, 2024', 'January 5, 2024', 'research', '', 'KRA 1. Education Planning  \r\nKRA 2. Research\r\nParticipation in the meeting aligns with Key Result Area (KRA) 1 in Education Planning and KRA 2 in Research. This showcases our commitment to contribute to regional discussions, providing inputs based on our experience and research in the field of education.\r\n', 'Number of Regional Level Meetings Attended', '1', '1', '100%', ' Successfully attended and contributed to the Regional Level Meeting, ensuring that the perspectives and experiences of the Schools Division of Davao Oriental were shared and considered in regional planning and research discussions. This also allowed us to gain insights from other divisions and incorporate best practices into our own strategies.', 'SGOD'),
(258, '2nd', '2023', 'June', '4', 'Research', 'Attended the Provincial Development Council Meeting to represent the SDS.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Honeys Hotel  Matiao,Mati City', 'June 21, 2023', 'June 21, 2023', 'research', '', 'KRA 1. Education Planning  \r\nAttending the meeting is part of the Key Result Area (KRA) 1 in Education Planning. The participation ensured that the Schools Division of Davao Oriental had a voice in the council and could represent its interests effectively.\r\n\r\n', 'Number of Provincial Level Meetings Attended', '1', '1', '100%', 'Successfully represented the Schools Division Superintendent at the Provincial Development Council Meeting, ensuring that the interests and views of the division were appropriately communicated and considered in the council\'s decisions and plans.', 'SGOD'),
