(322, '3rd', '2023', 'July', '1', 'Research', 'Facilitated and Evaluated  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental Via Online Google Form', 'Accomplishment', '', 'SEPS Planning and Research Frontline Services, performed routinely.', 'July 3-7, 2023', 'July 3-7, 2023', 'research', 'https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1V4njudbYXsdzFebqct_vBU-RSN9WovteWVftzSyXMKY/edit?usp=sharing', 'KRA 2. Research\r\n\r\n*Frontline Services to Researchers - Issuance of Permits to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental subject for SGOD Chief Review and SDS Approval ', 'Number of Permits Reviewed and Approved', '8', '8', '100%', 'Achieved a 100% completion rate in evaluating and approving permits for research, demonstrating our commitment to support and encourage research in the Division. This activity aligns with our Key Result Area (KRA) in research and emphasizes our proactive approach in promoting research culture. It also highlights our efficiency in handling and processing such requests, thereby ensuring researchers can begin their work without unnecessary delays. The approved research could contribute to the furth', 'SGOD'),
