(324, '3rd', '2023', 'July', '2', 'Research', 'Served as  Resource Speaker, Panelist and Training Manager:  Division Blended Seminar-Workshop In Crafting Research at  Baywalk Hotel Mati & Via VTC Platform.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Blended Mode: at Baywalk Hotel Mati  & via VTC Platform', 'July 13-15, 2023', 'July 13-15, 2023', 'research', '<iframe src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Falda.pawin.1%2Fposts%2F820467246407967&show_text=true&width=500\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share\"></iframe>', 'Contributed to Major Final Outputs (MFOs) in Education Governance: Key Result Area (KRA) 2 - Research and KRA 4 - Technical Assistance. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform.', '100% of  tasks Completed within the given schedule.', '1', '1', '100%', 'Successfully fulfilled all roles and responsibilities associated with the event. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform. Feedback from participants was overwhelmingly positive, indicating that the seminar-workshop was effective in enhancing their research crafting skills. Looking forward to supporting similar initiatives in the future to further strengthen our education system through evidence-based practices.', 'SGOD'),
