(361, '3rd', '2023', 'August', '2', 'Research', 'Facilitated and Evaluated  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental Via Online Google Form', 'Accomplishment', '', 'SEPS Planning and Research Frontline Services, performed routinely.', 'August 7-11, 2023', 'August 7-11, 2023', 'research', 'https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1V4njudbYXsdzFebqct_vBU-RSN9WovteWVftzSyXMKY/edit?usp=sharing', 'KRA 2. Research\r\n\r\n*Frontline Services to Researchers - Issuance of Permits to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental subject for SGOD Chief Review and SDS Approval ', 'Number of Permits Reviewed and Approved', '4', '4', '100%', 'Achieved a 100% completion rate in evaluating and approving permits for research, demonstrating our commitment to support and encourage research in the Division. This activity aligns with our Key Result Area (KRA) in research and emphasizes our proactive approach in promoting research culture. It also highlights our efficiency in handling and processing such requests, thereby ensuring researchers can begin their work without unnecessary delays. The approved research could contribute to the further improvement of educational practices and policies in our Division. We are eager to witness the impact of these research studies on the development of education in Davao Oriental.', 'SGOD'),
(362, '2nd', '2023', 'June', '4', 'Research', 'Prepared  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental for SGOD Chief review and SDS Approval.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'SEPS Planning and Research Frontline Services, performed routinely.', 'June 19-23, 2023', 'June 19-23, 2023', 'research', 'https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1a7l5pt29AJgwdaTjtTwi8biEYYVKr2x7?usp=sharing', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\n', 'Number of Approval Letters Prepared', '2', '2', '100%', 'Frontline services in research management: Evaluate requests for research permits and prepare  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research based on client demand. This task is part of the key responsibility areas (KRA) for research governance. It ensures that all research activities conducted in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental have been thoroughly reviewed and approved, maintaining high research standards. ', 'SGOD'),
