(481, '4th', '2023', 'October', '3', 'Research', 'Provided Technical Assistance Services to to Division Researchers in the Crafting of BERF FY2024  Basic/Action Research  Proposals and submitted 33   BERF FY2024  Division Basic/Action Research  Proposals to the Regional Research Committee.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Online & Face to Face TA Sessions', 'Oct 9-13,  2023', 'Oct 9-13,  2023', 'research', 'Note: MOVs via VTC Platform/ FB Messenger/GMail,  SMS and Pictures of Face to Face/In-Person Activity. \r\n', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\nKRA 4. Technical Assistance\r\n\r\n', 'Number of Researchers /Research Proposals/Studies  given Technical Assistance', '33', '33', '100%', 'Frontline Technical Assistance services of SEPS Planning and Research based on client requests. Successfully provided technical assistance to the division researchers as needed, focusing on the development of basic and action research proposals/studies. Each researcher had unique needs, and tailored assistance was provided accordingly. This included aspects such as research design, data analysis techniques, and best practices for academic writing. The guidance provided contributed significantly to the enhancement of research proposals/studies, and the researchers are now better equipped to conduct their respective studies. Feedback from the researchers was positive, with many expressing gratitude for the insightful assistance. Looking forward to seeing the impactful outcomes these research studies will bring to the education sector in our division.', 'SGOD'),
