(483, '3rd', '2023', 'September', '3', 'Research', 'Served as  Resource Speaker, Panelist and Training Manager:  DIVISION TRAINING-WORKSHOP ON ACTION RESEARCH FOR TEACHERS AND SCHOOL ADMINISTRATORS ACROSS LEARNING CURRICULUM - BLENDED LEARNING APPROACH on 15-17 September 2023 Via Virtual Platform  & Face To Face at the San Jose CES Activity Center, Caraga South District Office, Caraga, Davao Oriental ', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Via Virtual Platform  & Face To Face at the San Jose CES Activity Center, Caraga South District Office, Caraga, Davao Oriental', 'Sep. 15-17, 2023', 'Sep. 15-17, 2023', 'research', 'https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aHoCtLea4vuiyI2bVH2FrYVqhgqAj_X7-PaQ3lfX06U/edit?usp=sharing', 'Contributed to Major Final Outputs (MFOs) in Education Governance: Key Result Area (KRA) 2 - Research and KRA 4 - Technical Assistance. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform.', '100% of  tasks Completed within the given schedule.', '1', '1', '100%', 'Successfully fulfilled all roles and responsibilities associated with the event. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform. Feedback from participants was overwhelmingly positive, indicating that the seminar-workshop was effective in enhancing their research crafting skills. Looking forward to supporting similar initiatives in the future to further strengthen our education system through evidence-based practices.', 'SGOD'),
