(516, '1st', '2024', 'January', '2', 'Research', 'Served as  Resource Speaker &  Panelist: Presentation of Math Action Research Proposals in Collaboration with the CID & SDRMC-TWG-DEREG ', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Rexigels Place, Dahican, City of Mati,  Davao Oriental', 'January 6, 2024', 'January 6, 2024', 'research', '', 'Contributed to Major Final Outputs (MFOs) in Education Governance: Key Result Area (KRA) 2 - Research and KRA 4 - Technical Assistance. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform.', '100% of  tasks Completed within the given schedule.', '1', '1', '100%', 'Successfully fulfilled all roles and responsibilities associated with the event. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform. Feedback from participants was overwhelmingly positive, indicating that the seminar-workshop was effective in enhancing their research crafting skills. Looking forward to supporting similar initiatives in the future to further strengthen our education system through evidence-based practices.', 'SGOD'),
(517, '2nd', '2023', 'June', '5', 'Research', 'Attended the Provincial Statistics Committee Meeting to represent the SDS.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Honeys Hotel  Matiao,Mati City', 'June 26, 2023', 'June 26, 2023', 'research', '', 'KRA 1. Education Planning  \r\nAttending the meeting is part of the Key Result Area (KRA) 1 in Education Planning. The participation ensured that the Schools Division of Davao Oriental had a voice in the council and could represent its interests effectively.\r\n\r\n', 'Number of Provincial Level Meetings Attended', '1', '1', '100%', 'Successfully represented the Schools Division Superintendent at the Provincial Level Meeting, ensuring that the interests and views of the division were appropriately communicated and considered in the Provincial decisions and plans.', 'SGOD'),
(518, '3rd', '2023', 'September', '3', 'Research', 'Provided Technical Assistance Services to to Division Researchers in the Crafting of Basic/Action Research  Proposals/Studies.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Online & Face to Face TA Sessions', 'Sep. 16-22,  2023', 'Sep. 16-22,  2023', 'research', 'Note: MOVs via VTC Platform/ FB Messenger/GMail and SMS. \r\n', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\nKRA 4. Technical Assistance\r\n\r\n', 'Number of Researchers /Research Proposals/Studies  given Technical Assistance', '30', '30', '100%', 'Frontline Technical Assistance services of SEPS Planning and Research based on client requests. Successfully provided technical assistance to the division researchers as needed, focusing on the development of basic and action research proposals/studies. Each researcher had unique needs, and tailored assistance was provided accordingly. This included aspects such as research design, data analysis techniques, and best practices for academic writing. The guidance provided contributed significantly to the enhancement of research proposals/studies, and the researchers are now better equipped to conduct their respective studies. Feedback from the researchers was positive, with many expressing gratitude for the insightful assistance. Looking forward to seeing the impactful outcomes these research studies will bring to the education sector in our division.', 'SGOD'),
(519, '4th', '2023', 'October', '4', 'Research', 'Prepared  Official Communications and Division Memorandum for SGOD Chief review and SDS Approval.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'SEPS Planning and Research Frontline Services, performed routinely.', 'Oct 16-20  2023', 'Oct 16-20  2023', 'research', '', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\n', 'Number of Official Communications and Division Memorandum Prepared', '2', '2', '100%', 'Frontline services in research management: Evaluate requests for research permits and prepare  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research based on client demand.', 'SGOD'),
(520, '4th', '2023', 'October', '2', 'Research', 'Evaluated  Research Permit Documentary Requirements and Prepared  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental for SGOD Chief review and SDS Approval.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'SEPS Planning and Research Frontline Services, performed routinely.', 'Oct 2-5,  2023', 'Oct 2-5,  2023', 'research', 'https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1a7l5pt29AJgwdaTjtTwi8biEYYVKr2x7?usp=sharing', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\n', 'Number of Approval Letters Prepared', '3', '3', '100%', 'Frontline services in research management: Evaluate requests for research permits and prepare  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research based on client demand.', 'SGOD'),
