(568, '4th', '2023', 'October', '3', 'Social Mobilization and Networking', 'Prepared request for vehicle to PLGU to transport 750 sets of school supplies donated by the National Grid Corporation of the Philippines', 'Accomplishment', '', '', '', 'October 11, 2023', 'smn', '', '', 'Number of request documents prepared', '1', '1', '100%', 'Recipient schools are the following: (1) Sibajay ES-250 sets or 25 boxes , (2) San Rafael IS-250 sets or 25 boxes and (3) Ban-ao ES Baganga-250 sets or 25 boxes. To the recipient schools, you may claim the school supplies starting October 17-20, 2023 at the division office. Each box weighs 18.35 kls. Please submit the list of learner recipients of the school supplies, signed by the School Head.', 'SGOD'),
