(584, '4th', '2023', 'November', '4', 'Research', 'Served as  Training Manager:  Division Capacity Building for RESEARCH Science Technology Engineering Mathematics (STEM) Teachers Developing Science Investigatory Projects, Venue: Baywalk Hotel, Mati City, Davao Oriental  ', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Baywalk Hotel, City of Mati, ,  Davao Oriental', 'Sep. 28-30, 2023', 'November 25-27, 2023 ', 'research', '', 'Contributed to Major Final Outputs (MFOs) in Education Governance: Key Result Area (KRA) 2 - Research and KRA 4 - Technical Assistance. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform.', '100% of  tasks Completed within the given schedule.', '1', '1', '100%', 'Successfully fulfilled all roles and responsibilities associated with the event. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform. Feedback from participants was overwhelmingly positive, indicating that the seminar-workshop was effective in enhancing their research crafting skills. Looking forward to supporting similar initiatives in the future to further strengthen our education system through evidence-based practices.', 'SGOD'),
(585, '4th', '2023', 'October', '3', 'Research', 'Served as  Resource Speaker, Panelist and Training Manager:  Division Seminar-Workshop  on the Technical Assistance and Evaluation of BERF FY2024 Research Proposals and Evaluation of Completed BERF Manuscripts FY2016-2022 organized by the CID & SGOD in coordination with the Schools Division Research Management Committee on October 7-9, 2023 Via Online sessions via suitable VTC Platform & Face to Face Sessions (Live-Out) at the Madayaw Hall, DepED Davao Oriental Division Office ', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Via Virtual Platform  & Face To Face at Lupon West District Office,  Davao Oriental', 'October 7-9, 2023 ', 'October 7-9, 2023 ', 'research', '', 'Contributed to Major Final Outputs (MFOs) in Education Governance: Key Result Area (KRA) 2 - Research and KRA 4 - Technical Assistance. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform.', '100% of  tasks Completed within the given schedule.', '1', '1', '100%', 'Successfully fulfilled all roles and responsibilities associated with the event. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform. Feedback from participants was overwhelmingly positive, indicating that the seminar-workshop was effective in enhancing their research crafting skills. Looking forward to supporting similar initiatives in the future to further strengthen our education system through evidence-based practices.', 'SGOD'),
(586, '4th', '2023', 'November', '2', 'Research', 'Provided Technical Assistance Services to to Division Researchers in the Crafting of Basic/Action Research  Proposals/Studies.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Online & Face to Face TA Sessions', 'Nov. 6-10, 2023', 'Nov. 6-10, 2023', 'research', 'Note: MOVs via VTC Platform/ FB Messenger/GMail and SMS. \r\n', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\nKRA 4. Technical Assistance\r\n\r\n', 'Number of Researchers /Research Proposals/Studies  given Technical Assistance', '4', '4', '100%', 'Frontline Technical Assistance services of SEPS Planning and Research based on client requests. Successfully provided technical assistance to the division researchers as needed, focusing on the development of basic and action research proposals/studies. Each researcher had unique needs, and tailored assistance was provided accordingly. This included aspects such as research design, data analysis techniques, and best practices for academic writing. The guidance provided contributed significantly to the enhancement of research proposals/studies, and the researchers are now better equipped to conduct their respective studies. Feedback from the researchers was positive, with many expressing gratitude for the insightful assistance. Looking forward to seeing the impactful outcomes these research studies will bring to the education sector in our division.', 'SGOD'),
