(682, '4th', '2023', 'October', '1', 'Research', 'Served as  Resource Speaker, Panelist and Training Manager:  DIVISION TRAINING-WORKSHOP ON ACTION RESEARCH FOR TEACHERS AND SCHOOL ADMINISTRATORS ACROSS LEARNING CURRICULUM - BLENDED LEARNING APPROACH on 15-17 September 2023 Via Virtual Platform  & Face To Face at the San Jose CES Activity Center, Caraga South District Office, Caraga, Davao Oriental ', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Via Virtual Platform  & Face To Face at Lupon West District Office,  Davao Oriental', 'Sep. 28-30, 2023', 'Sep. 28-30, 2023', 'research', 'https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aHoCtLea4vuiyI2bVH2FrYVqhgqAj_X7-PaQ3lfX06U/edit?usp=sharing', 'Contributed to Major Final Outputs (MFOs) in Education Governance: Key Result Area (KRA) 2 - Research and KRA 4 - Technical Assistance. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform.', '100% of  tasks Completed within the given schedule.', '1', '1', '100%', 'Successfully fulfilled all roles and responsibilities associated with the event. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform. Feedback from participants was overwhelmingly positive, indicating that the seminar-workshop was effective in enhancing their research crafting skills. Looking forward to supporting similar initiatives in the future to further strengthen our education system through evidence-based practices.', 'SGOD'),
(683, '4th', '2023', 'November', '2', 'Research', 'Evaluated  Research Permit Documentary Requirements and Prepared  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research in the Schools Division of Davao Oriental for SGOD Chief review and SDS Approval.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'SEPS Planning and Research Frontline Services, performed routinely.', 'Nov. 6-10, 2023', 'Nov. 6-10, 2023', 'research', 'https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1a7l5pt29AJgwdaTjtTwi8biEYYVKr2x7?usp=sharing', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\n', 'Number of Approval Letters Prepared', '11', '11', '100%', 'Frontline services in research management: Evaluate requests for research permits and prepare  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research based on client demand.', 'SGOD'),
(684, '4th', '2023', 'November', '2', 'Research', 'Prepared  Official Communications and Division Memorandum for SGOD Chief review and SDS Approval.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'SEPS Planning and Research Frontline Services, performed routinely.', 'Nov. 6-10, 2023', 'Nov. 6-10, 2023', 'research', '', 'MFOs - Education Governance\r\nKRA 2. Research\r\n', 'Number of Official Communications and Division Memorandum Prepared', '4', '4', '100%', 'Frontline services in research management: Evaluate requests for research permits and prepare  Letter Approval of  Requests for Permit to Conduct Research based on client demand.', 'SGOD'),
