(704, '3rd', '2024', 'January', '2', 'Research', 'Received Plaque of Recognition during the  CY2023 PIR on Planning and Research. ', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Apo View Hotel, Davao City', 'January 18-19, 2024', 'January 18-19, 2024', 'research', '', 'KRA 1. Education Planning  \r\nKRA 2. Research\r\nParticipation in the meeting aligns with Key Result Area (KRA) 1 in Education Planning and KRA 2 in Research. This showcases our commitment to contribute to regional discussions, providing inputs based on our experience and research in the field of education.\r\n', 'Number of Regional Level Meetings Attended', '1', '1', '100%', ' Successfully attended and contributed to the Regional Level Meeting, ensuring that the perspectives and experiences of the Schools Division of Davao Oriental were shared and considered in regional planning and research discussions. This also allowed us to gain insights from other divisions and incorporate best practices into our own strategies.', 'SGOD'),
