(706, '4th', '2023', 'October', '3', 'Research', 'Served as  Resource Speaker, Panelist and Training Manager:  Division Level Training-Workshop on Action Research for Teachers and School Heads Across Learning Areas through Hybrid Learning Approach organized by the Cateel-2 District in coordination with the Schools Division Research Management Committee on October 13-15, 2023 Via Virtual Platform & Face To Face at Cateel-2 District, Davao Oriental', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Via Virtual Platform  & Face To Face at Lupon West District Office,  Davao Oriental', 'Oct 13-15,  2023', 'Oct 13-15,  2023', 'research', '', 'Contributed to Major Final Outputs (MFOs) in Education Governance: Key Result Area (KRA) 2 - Research and KRA 4 - Technical Assistance. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform.', '100% of  tasks Completed within the given schedule.', '1', '1', '100%', 'Successfully fulfilled all roles and responsibilities associated with the event. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform. Feedback from participants was overwhelmingly positive, indicating that the seminar-workshop was effective in enhancing their research crafting skills. Looking forward to supporting similar initiatives in the future to further strengthen our education system through evidence-based practices.', 'SGOD'),
