(827, '2nd', '2023', 'June', '2', 'Research', 'Served as  Resource Speaker: SEPS Rowil T: OB Resource Speaker: Division Seminar On Action Research For Teachers', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Blended Mode: at Manuel B. Guiñez Sr. National High School COMLAB 1 & via VTC Google Meet', 'June 8, 2023', 'June 8, 2023', 'research', 'https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F12PYOjKK-Sl1lYZ6iY5ZtoC9IIZ3Jzj7G%3Fusp%3Dsharing%26fbclid%3DIwAR3L8pwISdJ1cA2aquDA4xW3M4Mv5lVpHDQPKb3qLIutmo11a_SwogYmohs&h=AT2xOp4BWWvx8fR2M34tu7aPyk6tiww4ubfeuO7ctgT6x8XTkfTAS1qKTBuDDSxupzdb6ngsHGRISTL-odNP5Hrwoq7hXkqXAjsJfHDNjaGeAu50-6DT6mpseW0H1YgqiC3y0g', '', '100% of TA tasks Completed  within the given schedule', '1', '1', '100%', '', 'SGOD'),
(828, '1st', '2024', 'February', '1', 'Research', 'Served as  Resource Speaker &  Panelist: PACTIVITY TITLE	: Launching of PROJECT C.A.R.E. on January 30,  2024 at LUPON VOCATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL.', 'Accomplishment', '', 'Blended Mode / Online/Via VTC Platform', 'January 30,  2024', 'January 30,  2024', 'research', '', 'Contributed to Major Final Outputs (MFOs) in Education Governance: Key Result Area (KRA) 2 - Research and KRA 4 - Technical Assistance. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform.', '100% of  tasks Completed within the given schedule.', '1', '1', '100%', 'Successfully fulfilled all roles and responsibilities associated with the event. As a Resource Speaker, provided essential knowledge and skills on crafting research. As a Panelist, engaged in the critique and improvement of participants\' output. As a Training Manager, ensured the smooth flow of the event, and verified that all technical aspects worked flawlessly both on-site and on the virtual training conference (VTC) platform. Feedback from participants was overwhelmingly positive, indicating that the seminar-workshop was effective in enhancing their research crafting skills. Looking forward to supporting similar initiatives in the future to further strengthen our education system through evidence-based practices.', 'SGOD');
