(829, '1st', '2024', 'February', '1', 'Social Mobilization and Networking', 'Purchase of Paints from the additional donations for Brigada Eskwela ', 'Accomplishment', '', '', '', 'February 7, 2024', 'smn', '', '', 'No. of school recipients', '3', '3', '100%', 'The following schools of San Isidro North District are requested to claim their supplies at the Division Office: 1) Emilio Jacinto ES, 2)Maag ES and 3) Iba ES ', 'SGOD'),
(830, '1st', '2024', 'February', '1', 'Social Mobilization and Networking', 'Drafting of Memorandum in line with the preparations for PRIME-HRM Assessment Level III', 'Accomplishment', '', '', '', 'February 8, 2024', 'smn', '', '', 'No. of memoranda drafter', '1', '1', '100%', 'A conference of all PRIME HRM Committee, TWG members and Division IT personnel will be conducted on February 21 (Wednesday) 2024, 1:00 PM at Madayaw Hall, SDO Davao Oriental. Chairpersons of the Technical Woeking Groups for each PRIME HRM mechanism are expected to prepare a 5-minute presentation which  contains the 1) salient provisions of the policy in their assigned mechanism and 2) a list of tasks and activities that need to be conducted in line with the policy provisions.', 'SGOD'),
