(832, '1st', '2024', 'February', '1', 'Social Mobilization and Networking', 'Preparation of DepEd partnership Database Report for the month of January', 'Accomplishment', '', '', '', 'February 8, 2024', 'smn', '', '', 'No. of reports prepared', '1', '1', '100%', 'In compliance with DO 2 s. 2024 on the Removal of Administrative tasks from teachers, the encoding of school DepEd Partnership Database System reports shall now be accomplished by the School Head or any Non-teaching staff in the school. A link to the instructional videos on how to accomplish DPDS reports will be sent within the day.', 'SGOD'),
