(923, '1st', '2024', 'March', '5', 'Social Mobilization and Networking', 'Preparation for Brigada Eskwela SY 2024-2025', 'Updates', '', '', 'July 22-27, 2024', '', 'smn', '', 'Schools are directed to begin preparing for the Brigada Eskwela SY 2024-2025 through the conduct of School Needs Assessment using Brigada Eskwela Form 3. Preparations should be done prior to the end of the SY (May 31, 2024) in view of the provision in DO 3 s. 2024 that there will be no voluntary and mandatory tasks for teachers from June 1-30, 2024. There are still no specific guidelines yet for Brigada Eskwela 2024-2025 however, the External Partnerships Service announced that the guidelines shall be similar to the issued guidelines last year through DepEd Order 21 s. 2023.', '', '', '', '', '', 'SGOD'),
